item.title: Minnesota protesters, agents repeatedly square off while prosecutors quit after Renee Good’s death
item.description: Days of demonstrations against immigration agents and a new lawsuit have left Minnesota tense. Federal officers sprayed eye irritant and dropped tear gas at activists on Tuesday in Minneapolis.
